- 'top half of trade relationships' refers to the trade relationships with an export-import rank greater than 0.5;
- 'export-import rank' is a measure of the trade balance for each location and year, with higher values indicating a higher trade balance;
- 'premium users' refers to users with a subscription level of 'premium';
- The adjusted trade balance is used to evaluate the performance of the trade relationships.

